      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LIGHTNING LOTTE (6) doesn't win out of turn but recent form sound. Finished third (24.90) at this track last time making it two minors on end. Sure to be about the mark. TAW UNBOUND (8) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (30.31) last time in a Grade 5 at Nowra. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Cannot be left out. LOOPY EARS (2) comes off an average run last start when seventh at Nowra over 520m behind Spring Layla (30.45) in a Mix. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Deserves plenty of respect. MAGICAL GEM (7) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
